> > > -----Original Message-----
> > > From: Harshbarger, Robert [mailto:bharsh@puget.com]
> > > Sent: Friday, October 05, 2001 7:57 PM
> > > To: Rodriquez, Andy
> > > Cc: 'Hackney, Mark'; 'Grow, Lisa'; 'DEMPSEY, JERRY'; 'McIntosh, Jim';
> > > 'Lacen, Don'
> > > Subject: FW: WSCC Tagging practices
